display_long_description:
Gun X provides VR Gun shooting experience with lightning-fast gun assemblies, Duel Matches, frantic Zombie Mode and a Shooting Range for perfecting your aim. Challenge your friends and immerse yourself in an adrenaline-fueled fight.

[media]

Quickly assemble your gun to get the upper hand

[media]

Load your ammo and get ready 

[media]

Take aim and take down your opponent

[media]

Practice your skills and improve your aim

[media]

**Features:**
- Build your guns fast to outgun opponents.
- Multiplayer & Single Player
- Zombie Mode
- Shooting Range
- Duels

For more updates, join our discord (GunX-Lock n Load): https://discord.com/invite/Mf5RuEPNBn
